text.tspan: Elizabeth I
Regnans in Excelsis
Use the powers on the lowest rank
palace card
Use the powers on the rightmost yellow
card in your deck
If you have this in play when another
player wins the auction, you may take
any number of your exiled cards into
your hand
The Roaring Girl
Mary Frith
If you have this in play when you win
an auction, you may take any of the
cards you win directly into our hand
Use the powers on the lowest rank
non-red dungeon card
Outlaw
If the lowest rank played card is red,
earn 15 gold
Use the powers on the rightmost
non-red card in our deck
If the leftmost palace card is the same
color as the highest rank dungeon card
earn 15 gold
Storming of the Bastille
Women's March on Versailles
If you have this in play when you win
an auction, you may take any number of
cards from the dungeon into your hand
Statute of Labourers
Freemasonry
If you have this in play during the
auction, you may bid silver
Use the powers on the lowest rank
non-red played card with 1 or less
eyes
Earn 1 silver
Rocca Tower
Giustina Rocca
If you have this in play when you win
an auction, you may take cards from
the dungeon as well as the trial
Use the powers on the lowest rank
non-red palace card
Judge
Take a number of pawns into your
hand equal to the most eyes on any
played card
Phillip Marc
Nicola de la Haie
If you have this in play during the
auction, your bid is increased by 10
Use the powers on the highest rank
non-red dungeon card
Sheriff
Draw the rightmost card in your deck
